FBIS4-65947 "drweu102_k_94003" FBIS-WEU-94-102 Daily Report 25 May 1994 PORTUGAL Director Sworn In Director Sworn In LD2505133094 Lisbon Radio Renascenca in Portuguese to Europe 1030 GMT 25 May 94 LD2505133094 Lisbon Radio Renascenca Portuguese BFN [Excerpt] The new director general of the Portuguese secret services has been sworn in with the man who replaces him as head of the border and immigration services. The ceremony lasted a mere five minutes. Both Daniel Sanches and Lencastre Bernardo declined to talk to journalists. [passage omitted]
